n-V%C4%83n-Tr%E1%BB%A9/author-xpAnCf3fVJwFMTuePXmYuw">Trần Văn Trứ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng-Gi%E1%BB%9Bi-Th%E1%BA%A1ch/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-B%C3%ACnh-tr%E1%BA%A1m-c%E1%BA%A3m-ng%C3%A2m/poem-xemHyN9GOZJl_8S3PGsaiA">Thường Bình trạm cảm ngâm - 常平站感吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng-Gi%E1%BB%9Bi-Th%E1%BA%A1ch/author-bG25kGdlZ7zf1u6GUek6Iw">Tưởng Giới Thạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/Ti%E1%BB%85n-tr%C3%AD-s%E1%BB%B1-kinh-do%C3%A3n-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-C%C3%B4ng-Tr%E1%BB%A9/poem-NrIIAlUplVGXQz8y0KLfkA">Tiễn trí sự kinh doãn Nguyễn Công Trứ - 餞致事京尹阮公著</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-lfkyiRMg6zwt6_eiwas6Yg">Vũ Phạm Khải</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-Vi-Ph%C3%BAng-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-L%C3%A3ng-Ch%C3%A2u-l%E1%BB%A5c-s%E1%BB%B1-tham-qu%C3%A2n/poem-OWVAemeEA6UazTOSnqx8sg">Tống Vi Phúng thướng Lãng Châu lục sự tham quân - 送韋諷上閬州錄事參軍</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-T%C3%B4ng-Th%E1%BB%91c/Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam-th%E1%BA%BF-ch%C3%AD-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-pwYVzZ3mpuX7PHg6BRMRqA">Việt Nam thế chí tự - 越南世志序</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-T%C3%B4ng-Th%E1%BB%91c/author-AQI-nV6p-JhBHd--0I9cWA">Hồ Tông Thốc</a>)<br></div>	</div>
